在數學中，'''雙曲正弦'''是一種[[雙曲函數|雙曲函數]]，是[[雙曲幾何|雙曲幾何]]中，與歐幾里得幾何的[[正弦函數|正弦函數]]相對應的函數。雙曲正弦可以視為正弦函數的類似物，然而雙曲正弦不具備週期性，且在[[定義域|定義域]]為實數的情況下，其值域也包括了整個實數域。一般的正弦可以表示為單位圓上特定角構成之弦長的一半，或該角與圓之交點的y座標；而雙曲正弦則代表單位雙曲線上特定雙曲角構成之雙曲弦長的一半，或該雙曲角與單位雙曲線之交點的y座標。雙曲正弦一般以sinh表示<ref>(1999) ''Collins Concise Dictionary'', 4th edition, HarperCollins, Glasgow, {{ISBN|0 00 472257 4}}, p. 1386</ref>，在部分較舊的文獻中有時會以<math>\mathfrak{Sin}</math>表示。<ref>{{literatur| Autor = Dr. Franz Brzoska, Walter Bartsch| Titel = Mathematische Formelsammlung| Verlag = Fachbuchverlag Leipzig| Auflage= 2. verbesserte| Jahr = 1956}}</ref>

== 定義 ==
雙曲正弦一般計為<math>\sinh</math><ref>{{cite web|title=ISO 80000-2:2009|url=http://www.iso.org/iso/catalogue_detail?csnumber=31887|publisher=[[International_Organization_for_Standardization|International Organization for Standardization]]|accessdate=1 July 2010|archive-date=2014-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326013017/http://www.iso.org/iso/catalogue_detail?csnumber=31887|dead-url=no}}</ref>（有時會簡寫為<math>\operatorname{sh}</math><ref>{{cite book |author-first1=Izrail Solomonovich |author-last1=Gradshteyn |author-first2=Iosif Moiseevich |author-last2=Ryzhik |title=Table of Integrals, Series, and Products |publisher=[[Academic_Press,_Inc.|Academic Press, Inc.]] |date=2000 |edition=6 |isbn=978-0-12-294757-5 }}</ref>），其在複變分析中定義為:<ref name="Mathworld HyperbolicSine"/>
:<math>\sinh:z\mapsto\frac{\mathrm e^z-\mathrm e^{-z}}2</math>
其中<math>z\mapsto\mathrm e^z</math>是{{link-ja|複變指數函數|複素指数函数}}。
[[File:Complex_Sinh.jpg|left]]]]{{clear}}

也就是說，雙曲正弦等同於指數函數與其[[倒數|倒數]]之差的一半<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ww2.mathworks.cn/help/matlab/ref/sinh.html|title=sinh 双曲正弦|publisher=mathworks|access-date=2021-07-11|archive-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712135204/https://ww2.mathworks.cn/help/matlab/ref/sinh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雙曲正弦也可以視為[[指數函數|自然指數函數]]的{{link-en|函數的奇偶分解|Even–odd decomposition#Even–odd decomposition|奇函數部分}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://users.math.msu.edu/users/hensh/courses/133/fall2020/lectures/exam1/6.7.pdf|title=Even and Odd Parts of an Exponential Function|publisher=math.msu.edu|author=Richard Hensh|access-date=2021-07-11|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711023557/https://users.math.msu.edu/users/hensh/courses/133/fall2020/lectures/exam1/6.7.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在雙曲幾何中，雙曲正弦函數類似於歐幾里得幾何中的正弦函數。<ref name="mathworld, Hyperbolic Functions"/>

== 性質 ==
=== 一般性質 ===
*雙曲正弦在實數中是一個連續函數，在複數中是一個全純函數，因此在整個複數域中雙曲正弦處處可微，其導函數為[[雙曲餘弦|雙曲餘弦]]函數。<ref name="mathcentre.ac.uk">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mathcentre.ac.uk/resources/Engineering%20maths%20first%20aid%20kit/latexsource%20and%20diagrams/3_5.pdf|title=The hyperbolic functions|publisher=mathcentre.ac.uk|access-date=2021-07-11|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119153413/https://mathcentre.ac.uk/resources/Engineering%20maths%20first%20aid%20kit/latexsource%20and%20diagrams/3_5.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*雙曲正弦是一個奇函數。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.teaching.martahidegkuti.com/shared/lnotes/6_calculus/hyperbolic/hyperbolic1.pdf | title=Hyperbolic Functions | publisher=teaching.martahidegkuti.com | access-date=2021-09-15 | archive-date=2020-01-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113105652/http://www.teaching.martahidegkuti.com/shared/lnotes/6_calculus/hyperbolic/hyperbolic1.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>
*在實數域中，雙曲正弦是一個嚴格遞增函數。其中在區間<math>\left ] -\infty,0 \right [</math>上是[[凹函數|凹函數]]、在區間<math>\left ] 0,+\infty \right [</math>上是[[凸函數|凸函數]]。<ref name="mathcentre.ac.uk"/>

=== 三角學性質 ===
根據雙曲正弦與雙曲餘弦的指數定義，可以推得：<ref name="mathworld, Hyperbolic Functions">{{Cite mathworld|title=Hyperbolic Functions|urlname=HyperbolicFunctions|access-date=2020-08-29}}</ref><ref name="mathsisfun">{{Cite web|title=Hyperbolic Functions|url=https://www.mathsisfun.com/sets/function-hyperbolic.html|access-date=2020-08-29|website=www.mathsisfun.com|archive-date=2022-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303010839/https://www.mathsisfun.com/sets/function-hyperbolic.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
:<math>\mathrm e^z=\cosh z+\sinh z</math>
:<math>\mathrm e^{-z}=\cosh z-\sinh z</math>
其與經典的歐拉公式類似。

當<math>x\in\R</math>時，有以下恆等式:<ref name="mathworld, Hyperbolic Functions"/><ref name="Osborn, 1902" >{{Cite journal
 |first        = G.
 |last         = Osborn
 |jstor        = 3602492
 |title        = Mnemonic for hyperbolic formulae
 |journal      = [[The_Mathematical_Gazette|The Mathematical Gazette]]
 |page         = 189
 |volume       = 2
 |issue        = 34
 |date         = July 1902
 |doi          = 10.2307/3602492
 |url          = https://zenodo.org/record/1449741
 |access-date  = 2021-09-15
 |archive-date = 2021-11-01
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20211101114811/https://zenodo.org/record/1449741
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>
:<math>\sinh(\mathrm ix)=\frac{\mathrm e^{\mathrm ix}-\mathrm e^{-\mathrm ix}}2=\mathrm i\sin(x)</math> 
:<math>\sinh(x)=-\mathrm i\sin(\mathrm ix)</math><ref name="mathworld, Hyperbolic Functions"/>
:<math>\sinh(x+y)=\sinh(x)\cosh(y)+\cosh(x)\sinh(y)</math>
:<math>\sinh x=2\sinh\left (\frac {x} {2} \right )\cosh\left (\frac {x} {2} \right ) </math>
:<math>\sinh x=x\prod_{n=1}^\infty{\cosh\left (  x/2^n\right ) }</math>
:<math>\sinh^2\left(\frac x2\right)=\frac{\cosh(x)-1}2</math>

== 特殊值 ==
雙曲正弦存在一些特殊值<ref name="Mathworld HyperbolicSine">{{Cite Mathworld|title=Hyperbolic Sine|urlname=HyperbolicSine}}</ref>：
* <math>\sinh(0)=0</math>
* <math>\sinh(1)=\frac{\mathrm e^2-1}{2\mathrm e}</math>
* <math>\sinh(\mathrm i)=\mathrm i\sin(1)</math>
* <math>\sinh(\ln \varphi)=\frac{1}{2}</math>
其中<math>\varphi</math>為黃金比例

